# Browser profile sync exclusions (LibreWolf, Firefox, Brave, Chrome)
# Placed as .sync-exclude.lst in folders tagged "browser"
#
# Prevents SQLite database corruption when browser is open on multiple machines.
# Use xBrowserSync or native browser sync for bookmarks instead!
#
# Safe files that WILL still sync:
#   user.js, bookmarkbackups/, extensions/, extensions.json,
#   search.json.mozlz4, handlers.json

# ── SQLite databases — NEVER sync ──
*.sqlite
*.sqlite-wal
*.sqlite-shm
*.sqlite-journal

# ── Lock files ──
*.parentlock
.parentlock
lockfile
lock
SingletonLock
SingletonSocket
SingletonCookie

